      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非计划设立基础设施投资信托基金以吸引资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/s-africa-plans-infrastructure-investment-trusts-to-lure-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非计划成立基础设施投资信托并设立混合融资工具，吸引投资建设道路、输电网络和其他公共工程项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/s-africa-plans-infrastructure-investment-trusts-to-lure-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:04:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非不顾反对，考虑限制债务的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/s-africa-treasury-weighs-options-to-cap-debt-despite-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管遭到该国最大政党的反对，南非政府仍在考虑是否采取新的财政锚，为公共财政提供可持续的长期发展道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/s-africa-treasury-weighs-options-to-cap-debt-despite-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
